name: Asana Widget Playground
description:
Nothing great is made alone, so why should we manage our projects that way? Asana and Figma work together to help teams move work forward—no matter which tool they’re in.


This playground is designed to help you get started with the widget.


The Asana widget is licensed under Figma’s Terms of Service, unless you have a different agreement with us for Figma Services, and any use of Asana is subject to your agreement with Asana.
